  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>Guests staying at Il Castello will eat breakfast and dinner at the Italian restaurant, Cavalieri. You can also choose to eat in the Pineta, Forte Grill, Sardinian and Brazilian restaurants for no extra charge (reservations are required). The gourmet and à la carte restaurants require reservations and a supplement is payable.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
  <cateringShortDescription></cateringShortDescription>
