  <description><![CDATA[<p>Il Castello was completely refurbished in 2016 and offers an elegant and sophisticated accommodation. Rooms have been finished in a contemporary style with Sardinian features and fantastic views over the sea, mountains or gardens from spacious balconies. This luxurious hotel is just steps away from the sandy beach and guests of il Castello have exclusive access to a heated infinity pool on the edge of the white-sands.</p>
<p>The hotel is perfectly located to enjoy the resort’s facilities. Bandiere Bar, which is renowned for its signature cocktails, is overlooked by the hotel’s foyer and you’re within easy reach of gourmet restaurants. Castello can enjoy the charming Cavalieri Garden Restaurant with a Mediterranean buffet accompanied by soft live piano music or authentic recipes from Romagna at La Terrazza San Domenico, overseen by Chef Massimiliano Mascia (a supplement is payable locally).</p>]]></description>
